{"tid":1380544,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[時代革命] 經過呢兩個星期，我真係忍唔住要開post 講","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T02:18:41.000Z","uid":293227,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"72ff5483d5db4cd5a4a728ab2debda0202ba5bc7","tid":1380544,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"沙田新城市，警察沖入商場打人<br />\n<br />\n元朗地鐵站，同黑社會合作 ，刻意遲到唔救平民。<br />\n<br />\n全部警察開始唔帶委任証，用頭盔盾牌遮住樣，強光照記者，平射催淚彈，天橋瞄頭開槍，記者社工老人家女人照打，用私刑打被制服左既示威者，仲有好多好多。<br />\n<br />\n佢地Full Gear，就算比你地打贏佢，藍絲都會用文宣攻擊反攻。<br />\n<br />\n所以請立即停止所有示威式衝擊！！！因為示威好明顯已經冇用!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n要用其他方法!!!!!!! #老豆搵仔 #游擊 #真正be water<br />\n<br />\n要佢地放工好驚，要佢地知道禍必及妻兒，多行不義必自斃！！<br />\n<br />\n請各位勇武大哥們，開始試下用其他形式做勇武，停止送頭，好心痛!!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n不割"},{"pid":"a12f5360138f5ce10fc383a7902fbf5165c6a086","tid":1380544,"uid":65196,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T05:05:14.000Z","msg":"冇錯，已經出到最大火力，道德都負埋分<br />\n<br />\n係時接放工<br />\n<br />\n麻包袋"},{"pid":"46679f1cbdf02d6013a0abe84a2dd4a584773579","tid":1380544,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:04:13.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2d357970bf9bb0445cdc294a52e6eb237c81ed64","tid":1380544,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"雖然p牌 但我認同"},{"pid":"2f8f8e7667d9e32713c22c81bb49f7f3494a8317","tid":1380544,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d357970bf9bb0445cdc294a52e6eb237c81ed64","tid":1380544,"uid":5258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:05:15.000Z","msg":"雖然p牌 但我認同"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"我知大家唔鐘意聽P牌講野，但我facebook 好少勇武friend。一定要開個ac 同勇武義士講！！！<br />\n<br />\n打仗從來都係弱點攻擊，唔會硬碰。天琦講左，我地唔係要對賭，我地係要贏！！！<br />\n<br />\n啲狗最弱係放工之後！！大家集思廣益！！一定要清算佢地！！<br />\n<br />\n幫我推比勇武大哥們睇呀ching！！"},{"pid":"a30b8ff9fb7f604bf14edcbfeed8192df0e36357","tid":1380544,"uid":5258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:22:18.000Z","msg":"各位前線 得閒睇下吹水台 唔好剩係睇熱門呀"},{"pid":"cf7419e8af0883624fcc052dc97f6427b300ab57","tid":1380544,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:28:01.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"379ee410fcb8b4ac831e31c70d788b90f3d330b7","tid":1380544,"uid":182997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZvfrshB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvfrshB.png&h=3752f4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aGeG0CC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaGeG0CC.png&h=9e732aea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M1Fi2QX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM1Fi2QX.png&h=7fa45a28&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b76264d2011a5c957eac014cf3593ccb667f9eec","tid":1380544,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"再自推"},{"pid":"96aaa3186d19189a8dba5c90c7bda73dfcd16e83","tid":1380544,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"推到各位勇武大哥見到為止！！"},{"pid":"8bc0b43f661093a2c4b3614765ea65acfddb5d72","tid":1380544,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T02:18:41.000Z","msg":"再推!!!!"}]}